On the issue detail screen, the item in the "More" menu for "Create linked issue" is missing when the project type is "Software".

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This bug report is for *JIRA Software Cloud*. Using *JIRA Software Server*? [See the corresponding bug report|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JSWSERVER-13603].
  {panel}

h3. Problem Definition
Current behavior of columns under the *Column management* Section of board configuration:
- https://confluence.atlassian.com/jirasoftwarecloud/configuring-columns-764477997.html
-- {color:#205081}Not Started: Blue (Far Left){color}
-- {color:#f6c342}In Progress: Yellow (All columns between){color}
-- {color:#8eb021}Done: Green (Right Most Column){color}

This color Scheme is not reflected in the column headers for the Active sprint view

h3. Suggested Solution
It would be useful to be able to toggle the column header color on or off in active sprint view to reflect column color headers in the *Column management* section for visual reference.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This bug report is for *JIRA Software Cloud*. Using *JIRA Software Server*? [See the corresponding bug report|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JSWSERVER-13539].
  {panel}

